subtitleNullable: IMDb ratings of 1064 episodes of One piece
descriptionNullable:
This dataset was made based on [this ](https://isabella-b.com/blog/scraping-episode-imdb-ratings-tutorial/) great tutorial of webscraping, only adapting it to the One piece anime. The data was scraped from IMDb on May 31, 2023.
Note that episodes from 2 to 32 are missing due to not being included on IMDb list of episodes.
